Project Description
A console application in C++ that allows you to manage a database of instruments. The program allows adding, editing, deleting and searching for instruments. 
It supports garbage can operations, selected items and saving to files.

Functions
Managing instruments: Adding, editing, deleting.
Trash: Moving items to the trash, restoring, permanently deleting.
Marking: Marking instruments for further operations.
Sorting and searching: Sort by name, price, number of items; search by name and price.
File management: Saving and loading the database into files.
Translated with DeepL.com (free version)
